data.description: Welcome home! This lovely 3 bedroom Ranch features a spacious living room with a gas fireplace and vaulted ceilings. In the kitchen you are welcomed to a light and bright breakfast nook and a beautiful bay window. Just a few steps away you have access to the oversized concrete patio and a fenced in back yard. The main bedroom retreat includes a walk-in closet and its own private bathroom with a stand-up shower. Brand new windows and carpet have recently been installed throughout the entire home! Furnace replaced this year, Hot Water Heater in 2020. Pull into your 2-car garage which then leads you in the laundry/mudroom area. Close to shopping, Peterson AFB, Shriever SFB, Restaurants and Theaters! This home is sure to check all your boxes! Book your showing today!
